programme.title: World Watch: Forbidden History Ep7
programme.desc: Dokumentari bersama Jamie Theakson yang menyiasat mitos dan lagenda menarik dari sejarah. Jamie dan pasukan penyelidik merungkai misteri yang membentuk budaya masyarakat setempat. Dalam episod kali ini, Jamie melakukan kajian mengenai Johan Reichhart, seorang pemimpin tentera Nazi yang bertanggungjawab ke atas pembunuhan terhadap beribu-ribu tahanan perang sewaktu Perang Dunia Ke-2. Selepas perang tamat, Johan telah didakwa sebagai penjenayah perang.

programme.title: Bidadari: Rumah Kasih Suraya Ep2
programme.desc: Suraya Hanis, bekas peragawati, membuka Rumah Kasih Suraya menjelang ramadan. Didorong rasa tanggungjawab dan keinsafan, kisah ini bukan sahaja menggambarkan pengorbanannya untuk membantu insan memerlukan, tetapi juga menyingkap cabaran sebenar kerjaya selebriti yang sering dilihat glamor, namun penuh fitnah, godaan, dan memerlukan keimanan, ketabahan mental, serta usaha gigih untuk berjaya. Dalam episod ini tentang Syafiq seorang pemasang tenaga solar telah dipilih untuk bekerja di Rumah Kasih Suraya secara sambilan kerana kemahiran yang dia ada. Syafiq meminati Suraya sejak dia kecil lagi. Cik Tim tidak suka Primadona Zaiton tinggal di RKS kerana menurutnya Primadona Zaiton pernah mengambil barang dan gila. Pelakon: Nad Zainal, Fauziah Ahmad Daud, Fad Anuar, Dato Jalalauddin Hassan, Nor Albaniah, Sobri Anuar, dan Adam Shahz.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Resort Kasih Bunga Raya Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kisah suka duka kehidupan sebagai pekerja resort yang muhibah. Ali, Santi dan Teong telah berjaya melepasi temuduga dan mula berkhidmat di Resort Kasih Bunga Raya. Namun kehadiran seorang tetamu yang cerewet telah menduga mereka. Swee Lan mengajar mereka bertiga membuat kerja-kerja pejabat. Dalam masa yang sama ada wartawan yang ingin menemuramah kakitangan resort. Hasbullah, Swee Lan dan Mariam berusaha berlatih bercakap sebagai persediaan untuk ditemuramah. Pelakon: Roy Azman, Mustaqim Bahadon, Tash Yong, Thiyagaraja Marimuthu, Derek Yifan, Rahim Omar, Melanie Tan, C.Vasantihakumaran, Aman Nassim, Nazia Mustafar, Tony Eusoff, Monica Picca, Rosli Rahman Adam, dan Zalfa Zin.

programme.title: Spektra: Kau? C.E.O Aku? Ep20
programme.desc: Aisya berkahwin dengan Danial atas pilihan keluarga, namun perkahwinan mereka terganggu akibat kehadiran Mila, teman rapat Danial. Setelah kehilangan anak, Danial memutuskan untuk berkahwin dengan Mila, sementara Aisya terpaksa menerima keputusan itu. Namun, Aisya mendapat sokongan teman-temannya, Anis, Syafiq, dan Hakimi, yang berusaha memperjuangkan haknya. Dalam episod ini Danial syak Hakimi yang menyebabkan Aisya keguguran setelah Pak Hamid memberitahu ada kereta yang beberapa kali lalu di rumah Danial. Danial selalu keluar bersama Mila. Mila merasakan rancangannya untuk memiliki Danial semakin berjaya. Danial tidak melayan Aisya dengan mesra kerana dapat tahu yang Aisya tidak boleh mengandung lagi. Pelakon: Azrel Ismail, Puteri Aishah, Syazwan Zulkifly, Neera Azizi, Talha Harith, Siti Hariesa, Trisha Ooi, Zuhairi Ibrahim, Anne Abdullah, Amelina, Ainina Ahmad, dan Zalfa Zin

programme.title: Simfoni Alam Ep15
programme.desc: Dokumentari memaparkan isu hidupan liar dan alam semulajadi. Terumbu karang di negara ini sedang mengalami isu kelunturan besar-besaran (mass coral bleaching) akibat peningkatan suhu permukaan laut yang boleh memberi implikasi seerius terhadap biodiversiti marin, perikanan terumbu karang dan pelancongan di Malaysia. Lebih 50 peratus terumbu karang di beberapa tapak terumbu seperti Pulau payar, pulau Perhentian, dan Pulau Tioman terjejas teruk.

programme.title: Catatan Seorang Da’i Ep8
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang ustaz muda, Muhammad Syiffa yang tidak pernah jemu-jemu berdakwah dari satu masjid ke satu masjid. Dalam melaksanakan usaha dakwahnya itu, beliau telah berdepan dengan pelbagai peristiwa yang memberikan isyarat kepada umat manusia tentang tanda-tanda awal kiamat. Sebagai pendakwah juga Syiffa berusaha menyelesaikan masalah yang berlaku sehinggakan adakalanya nyawanya sendiri hampir menjadi taruhan. Selain itu, sebagai manusia biasa Syiffa turut berdepan dengan masalah dalam rumahtangganya dengan Aisyah yang membabitkan emosi. Dalam episod ini tentang orang kampung terlibat dengan perjudian sabung ayam termasuklah Sudin. Isteri Sudin, Leha mahu keluar dari rumah kerana tidak tahan dengan sikap Sudin. Borhan, ayah mertua Ustaz Syiffa terlibat dengan ajaran sesat.

programme.title: Beautiful Semporna Ep9
programme.desc: Meninjau keindahan pantai dan laut yang menjadi sumber pendapatan utama serta daya tarikan pelancong ke daerah ini, keunikan hidupan marin juga antara anugerah yang tidak ternilai. Episod kali ini memaparkan industri kraftangan kecil masyarakat Bajau dan ukiran kayu di Semporna serta hasil kraftangan wanita di Pulau Omadai.

programme.title: Tamadun Yang Hilang Ep8
programme.desc: Dokumentari khas yang memaparkan sebuah pengembaraan ilmu sejarah Islam silam, satu tamadun yang hilang (Maghribi & Andalus). Secara retrospektifnya, Al Fadhil Ustaz Ezad Azraai Jamsari dan Prof Madya Dr Zamri Arifin (UKM) dijemput sebagai pakar rujuk bidang- berkaitan khazanah ilmu dan informasi berkaitan tamadun yang hilang di bumi Semenanjung Iberia (Sepanyol & Portugal). Saksikan tentang kerajaan Al-Andalus- Kegemilangan dan Kejatuhan.

Merangkumi semua aspek pengisian ilmu agama, drama, nyanyian, hiburan, lawak spontan dan lain-lain, program ini menjadi pilihan penonton ketika berkumpul seisi keluarga menjelang waktu berbuka puasa. programme.title: Rumah Kasih Suraya Ep3
programme.desc: Suraya Hanis, bekas peragawati, membuka Rumah Kasih Suraya menjelang ramadan. Didorong rasa tanggungjawab dan keinsafan, kisah ini bukan sahaja menggambarkan pengorbanannya untuk membantu insan memerlukan, tetapi juga menyingkap cabaran sebenar kerjaya selebriti yang sering dilihat glamor, namun penuh fitnah, godaan, dan memerlukan keimanan, ketabahan mental, serta usaha gigih untuk berjaya. Dalam episod ini tentang Primadoza Zaiton ternampak Datuk Badar dari jendela biliknya. Dia kelihatan marah dan ingin bangun dari kerusi rodanya. Cik Tim melihat perbuatan Primadona Zaiton dari luar biliknya. Cik Tim memberitahu Kak Kiah yang Primadona Zaiton gila dan patut dihantar ke rumah sakit jiwa. Cik Tim telah menggeledah laci Kak Sal dan mengambil ubat. Cik Tim telah meletakkan ubat itu dalam air minuman Primadona Zaiton yang dibuat oleh Kak Sal namun Budin yang dahaga telah meminumnya. Pelakon: Nad Zainal, Fauziah Ahmad Daud, Fad Anuar, Dato Jalalauddin Hassan, Nor Albaniah, Sobri Anuar, dan Adam Shahz.

programme.title: Terjebak Nostalgia
programme.desc: Raisa (Raisa Andriana) dan Sora (Maruli Tampubolon) menjalin hubungan cinta yang erat. Sora, seorang pianis berbakat, mendapat peluang melanjutkan pengajian muzik di Juilliard School of Music, New York. Mereka berpisah dengan janji untuk bersatu semula selepas Sora menamatkan pengajiannya. Namun, selepas dua tahun, Sora hilang tanpa jejak akibat Badai Sandy di New York. Raisa, yang sukar melupakan Sora, mula menghantar surat dalam botol ke laut dan secara ajaib menerima balasan dari New York. Dengan bantuan sahabatnya, Reza (Chicco Jerikho), Raisa pergi ke New York untuk mencari Sora. Di sana, Raisa dan Reza melalui pelbagai pengalaman yang menguji perasaan dan hubungan mereka, membawa Raisa kepada penemuan tentang cinta dan masa lalunya.

programme.title: 11 Cinta Sebelum Kamu
programme.desc: Ray, selepas melamar Khadeja, Ray bertemu bakal ibu mentuanya, Dato' Shikin, seorang ibu tunggal dan peguam terkenal. Tanpa mengetahui latar belakang keluarga Khadeja, Ray mendapati bahawa Dato' Shikin telah menyelidik kehidupan masa lalunya yang 'nakal. Demi mendapatkan restu bagi mengahwini Khadeja, Dato Shikin telah menetapkan satu syarat, Ray perlu berdepan dan meminta maaf kepada kesemua 11 bekas teman wanitanya, merakam setiap kemaafan yang diberikan kepada Ray, dan menghantarnya kepada Dato' Shikin dalam tempoh 30 hari. Terdesak, Ray bersetuju dengan syarat tersebut dan meminta bantuan rakan baiknya, Kamil. Misi menjadi rumit apabila Ray dan Kamil mendapati bekas-bekas teman wanitanya, pesakit mental, jurulatih MMA, pegawai polis narkotik, barista kafe, penjaga zoo, pengusaha makanan dan pelbagai lagi, kesemuanya masih marah dengan Ray, terutamanya Aisha, kenalan rapat Ray dari bangku sekolah yang juga kononnya salah seorang dari 11 orang bekas kekasih Ray. Kali terakhir Ray bertemu dengan Aisha adalah 13 tahun lepas. Aisha menyedari bahawa Ray benar-benar telah berubah dan memutuskan untuk membantu Ray menyelesaikan misinya. Ray dan Aisha secara tidak diduga mula jatuh hati antara satu sama lain. Perasaan yang sama dirasai mereka 13 tahun lepas namun dipendam sehingga kini. Tanpa pengetahuan Ray, Dato' Shikin telah mengupah seseorang yang rapat dengan Ray untuk menggagalkan misinya. Masa 30 hari kian hampir tamat, dan Aisha merupakan orang yang terakhir dalam misi Ray untuk memohon kemaafan

programme.title: Epilog Yasmin
programme.desc: Telefilem Epilog Yasmin mengisahkan tentang Yasmin dan Nasir, pasangan yang sudah bertunang dan bakal berkahwin. Nasir merupakan seorang penulis dan sering berkongsi impiannya bersama Yasmin. Nasir sering menyatakan bahawa novel tulisanya akan menjadi sebuah novel "hot seller". Yasmin hanya ketawakan sahaja impian tunangnya itu kerana menganggap impian Nasir hanyalah sebuah angan-angan. Pada suatu hari, Nasir kemalangan dan meninggal dunia tanpa sempat menyiapkan novel karangannya. Selepas kematian Nasir, Yasmin berusaha menyiapkan novel tersebut demi sebuah cinta.

programme.title: Secebis Rindu Ep9
programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya dan Syed Reeza mula berkenalan melalui SMS, membina hubungan cinta walaupun Rasya mengalami paranoia dan Reeza dikenali sebagai lelaki yang suka menggoda. Hubungan mereka diuji apabila Rasya sukar mempercayai Reeza, dipengaruhi masa lalunya dan hasutan Adri, rakan Reeza. Akhirnya, Rasya berkahwin dengan Fahmi, sepupu dan pilihan keluarganya, tetapi perkahwinan itu gagal. Reeza yang terluka terpaksa bertunang dengan Hilda, pilihan keluarganya. Namun, perasaan mereka berdua kembali bercambah selepas bertemu semula di Dubai. Rasya berasa bersalah atas kesilapan lalu tetapi akhirnya mereka berjaya mengatasi salah faham dan ketakutan yang menghalang cinta mereka. Rancangan Reeza untuk menguji perasaan Rasya berjaya memecahkan ego dan ketakutannya. Mereka akhirnya berkahwin dan mendapat restu keluarga, membuktikan cinta sejati mereka mampu bertahan walaupun diuji pelbagai cabaran.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep8
programme.desc: Imran membunuh Ajeeb dan Uzair bersumpah untuk membalas dendam. Tanpa berfikir panjang Hatta mahu segera menyerang Imran tetapi Uzair mahu memastikan rakan-rakannya selamat. programme.desc: Michelle memarahi Din atas kehancuran yang ditimbulkannya dalam hidup mereka, ini jugak mengakibatkan Elyn untuk melakukan keputusan yang diraguinya sendiri.

programme.title: Taken
programme.desc: Seorang ejen CIA yang telah bersara mengembara merentasi Eropah dan menggunakan kemahiran lamanya untuk menyelamatkan anak perempuannya yang telah lama terpisah, yang diculik semasa dalam perjalanan ke Paris.

programme.title: Three Days To Kill
programme.desc: Seorang ejen perisikan antarabangsa yang berbahaya bertekad untuk meninggalkan kehidupannya yang penuh risiko demi membina hubungan yang lebih rapat dengan isteri dan anak perempuannya yang telah lama terpisah. Tetapi terlebih dahulu, dia perlu menyelesaikan satu misi terakhir walaupun itu bermakna dia perlu menguruskan dua tugas paling sukar setakat ini: memburu pengganas paling kejam di dunia dan menjaga anak perempuannya yang remaja buat pertama kali dalam sepuluh tahun, sementara isterinya tiada di bandar.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil 2
programme.desc: Kisah mengenai Fadil yang terjerumus ke dalam dunia mafia yang diketuai oleh Taji Samprit dan anaknya, Wak Doyok. Satu insiden menyebabkan Inspektor Wahab dan Inspektor Shuib mengesyaki Fadil sebagai Tiger, seorang pembunuh upahan profesional.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep8
programme.desc: Akhirnya dengan keupayaan yang mereka ada, mereka berhubung dengan hantu buaian(yang sering menyanyikan lagu buaibuaiku laju pada malam hari).

programme.title: Raging Phoenix
programme.desc: Sekumpulan penjahat menculik dan membunuh wanita di sekitar Thailand. Sanim dan rakan-rakannya, setelah orang tersayang diculik, telah bergabung untuk memecahkan kumpulan penculik. Dalam percubaan penculikan yang gagal, Deu telah diselamatkan oleh anak kapal Sanim. Selepas mempelajari gaya seni mempertahankan diri mereka yang unik, Deu membantu memikat kumpulan itu ke dalam pertempuran epik untuk menyelamatkan wanita di seluruh Thailand.

programme.title: Khun Pan 2
programme.desc: Cerita ini mengisahkan tentang seorang pegawai polis bernama Khun Phan dalam Perang Dunia Kedua. Dia menjalankan misi penyamaran untuk menumpaskan seorang gabenor di sebuah pulau yang semua orang di sana dianggap penyamun.

programme.title: Vengeance Of An Assassin
programme.desc: The Assassins' Code - Berpegang teguh pada misi. Jangan sekali-kali mengalihkan pandangan anda dari sasaran. Tidak menunjukkan belas kasihan. Natee (Dan Chupong) menjadi pembunuh kerana satu sebab- untuk mengetahui siapa yang membunuh ibu bapanya. Apabila dia semakin hampir untuk mendedahkan rangkaian rahsia kuasa dan rasuah, dia melakukan dua kali ganda dalam kerja, menjadikannya sasaran dan meletakkan semua orang yang dia sayangi dalam bahaya. Dikhianati, didedahkan dan diburu oleh pembunuh paling maut dalam perniagaan, kini Natee mempunyai kod baharu. Jadi lebih pantas. Lebih kuat. Pukul lebih kuat. Bertahan.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Lampir
programme.desc: Sekumpulan rakan yang sedang menjalani sesi fotografi pra-perkahwinan di sebuah vila mewah dan klasik secara tidak sengaja terperangkap di sarang suci Mak Lampir, yang dikatakan mendambakan kecantikan abadi. Mampukah mereka bertahan dalam permainan maut Mak Lampir?

programme.title: Mercury Man
programme.desc: Selepas memberus dirinya dengan bahan pelik, rata-rata anggota bomba berubah menjadi sesuatu yang jauh lebih hebat daripada dirinya seperti Mercury Man. Dikurniakan kuasa besar yang hebat, dia kini akan menggunakan kebolehannya untuk membantu menakluki kuasa jahat.

programme.title: Mock 2 For 3

programme.title: Tak Habis Fikri Ditembak Cinta Supir

programme.title: Cinta Setelah Cinta S2 Ep51
programme.desc: Starla menyangka dia telah menghadapi segalanya, tetapi penipuan Niko jauh lebih mendalam daripada yang disangkanya. Ketika dia terus berusaha mempertahankan perkahwinannya, ancaman baharu muncul. Ayu, yang masih taksub dengan Niko, semakin mengikatnya dalam perangkap dengan menggunakan anak mereka yang belum lahir sebagai umpan. Pada masa yang sama, naluri Starla merasakan ada sesuatu yang tidak kena, dan dia mula diburu oleh bayang-bayang serta rahsia gelap. Dengan keluarganya di ambang bahaya dan emosinya semakin tertekan, adakah Starla mampu melindungi orang-orang tersayang? Atau adakah pengkhianatan Niko akan mendorongnya melangkaui batas yang tidakbolehkembali?

programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Hot Door Night (M) Ep2307
programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: 100% Wife (T) Ep242
programme.desc: Three generations of the Jin family live under one roof. Mrs. Jin-Ke mei-man has two sons, You-Tsai and You-De. You-Tsai abandoned the family many years ago, leaving his wife Siou-Ying to shoulder the huge responsibility of the Jin family business selling fish products at market. Although Siou-Ying was betrayed by You-Tsai, she has still been a dutiful daughter to her mother-in-law, and has single-mindedly raised four children.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan (T) Ep5055
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: In the Mood for Love
programme.desc: This movie is Wong Kar Wais most acclaimed feature, navigating the subtle love relationship between Chow Mo Wan and Su Li Zhen after both discover their spouses having an affair with each other.

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 2
programme.desc: Fanny appears to be an ordinary housewife but is in fact a mahjong expert. Deeply in love with her husband, she loses to a seductive woman, Curvy, both on the mahjong table and in competing for her husbands love. With the help from her mahjong master, Fanny vows to take on Curvy in the Mahjong King tournament!

programme.title: Love Never Ends
programme.desc: An empty-nest elderly man and a widowed elderly woman who collects scrap, meet unexpectedly and gradually develop feelings for each other. An elderly couple whose wife suffers from a serious illness, makes a living by selling scrap. Both these elderly couples fall deeply in love and prove that love never ends, even if there is no tomorrow!

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong
programme.desc: Ng Shun and his family return to the public housing estate where he grew up, not to visit his aging father, but to seek refuge after his business has failed. When his family of five squeeze into the small estate unit, Ng Shun is forced to face his long-neglected family problems...

programme.title: Dragon Tiger Gate
programme.desc: Adapted from a famous Hong Kong comic, Tiger Wong is ambushed after he unwittingly took the Lousha Plaque but is saved by his brother Dragon Wong. They also befriended Turbo Shek during the fight and the trio forms a brotherhood. To avenge the death of the Dragon Gate masters, they train and vow to defeat Shibumi, the leader of Lousha Clan.

programme.title: Kungfu Stuntmen
programme.desc: Hong Kong action cinema is famous for its real kung fu moves performed by a group called Kung Fu Stuntmen. This docu-film pays tribute to the generations of kung fu stuntmen, with the crew spending over two years digging archives and interviewing many talents, including the most prominent masters like Jackie Chan, Donnie Yen and Sammo Hung.

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: Tainted Love
programme.desc: Office lady Zhou Ran falls victim to an online dating love scam and is cheated of 550,000 yuan. Following faint clues left by the scammer, Zhou Ran comes to a small coastal town and encounters two young men. She gradually discovers that these two men have hidden the clues of the scam, and sets out on her revenge plan.

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Founded in the 70s, Hong Kongs ICAC is committed to fight corruption in the police force. Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end. Where the wind blows, Hong Kong is no longer what it used to be!

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: The Lady Iron Chef
programme.desc: Beer girl and part-time model Ceci has terrible cooking skills. Coming from a well-off family that owns a big culinary business, wealthy SK meets Ceci in a gourmet competition held by his family's company. Despite their different backgrounds, Ceci and SK fall for each other. However, SK's dominating mother disapproves of their relationship. To win over her future mother-in-law, Ceci must beat her rival Jade in a gourmet showdown

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Break Up Club
programme.desc: Joe is a 20-something slacker who only takes one thing seriously: his on-and-off girlfriend Flora. After their latest breakup, Joe goes to an audition for a documentary by director Barbara Wong. Handed a camera, Joe records his discovery of a magical website that reunites him with Flora at the price of breaking up his best friend and his girlfriend. However, despite the efficiency of the website, Joe's refusal to change his immature ways and Flora's attraction to a talented graffiti artist threatens to break them up once more.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack

programme.title: The Italian Recipe
programme.desc: Famous pop idol Peng travels to Rome for a reality show and encounters an ordinary girl, Mang, who dreams of becoming a great chef after migrating to Italy. Peng and Mang have nothing in common but spend a magical night in Rome together. Their lives begin to change as the two start to fall in love.

programme.title: CJ7
programme.desc: Stephen Chow returns in this hilarious and heartwarming tale of a father and son who discover an adorable alien in the trash.

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover to a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Midnight Fly
programme.desc: With her marriage in crisis, Michele takes off to Europe for a vacation and meets a Japanese woman named Miki. As they become friends and travel together, Michele discovers that Miki is her husband's mistress. When Miki goes missing in Morocco, Michele does everything she can to find her but ends up paying a heavy price

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Dailys Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: CJ7
programme.desc: Stephen Chow returns in this hilarious and heartwarming tale of a father and son who discover an adorable alien in the trash.

programme.title: The Fierce Wife
programme.desc: An Zhen divorces her husband after his infidelity but faces a pivotal decision four years later - to return to her cheating husband and old life or to embark on a new life with a new love?

programme.title: Happy Dragons
programme.desc: Four retired secret agents embark on a quest for the "Golden Relic" triggered by a mahjong game. Their journey unexpectedly transports them back 30 years, restoring their youth. While striving to rectify their past mistakes, the agents unravel a hidden conspiracy along the way.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: Invisible Target
programme.desc: Three young police officers driven by different motives decide to join forces to defeat Tien and his lethal, mercenary gang. As they team up to prevent another massive robbery, they discover that it is instigated by another unknown man. With courage, wits and dexterity, the trio are determined to not let Tien and the instigator escape.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Set in 2020 during the outbreak of COVID-19, the movie features interconnected stories of three women's lives as they navigate the uncertain future amongst their respective friends and families. From the struggles at home to challenges in relationships and conflicts at work, these three women rise with strength when faced with plights unknown.

programme.title: Dust to Dust
programme.desc: Back in 1995, the Police successfully arrested five armed bank robbers while the two masterminds got tipped off and made a clean escape. Decades later, retired cop Wang Shou Yue is drawn back to the unsolved case when he sees a blurred figure in a news clip. A battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: In this prequel, the secrets of Infernal Affairs are revealed - the resentment between police superintendent Wong and crime boss Sam, as well as the beginning of the parallel fates of the two moles, Yan and Ming. The keys lie in the hands of Sam's wife, a ruthless kingpin and a righteous cop.

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her fathers towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: The Black Lizard
programme.desc: Young swordsman Lung Fei encounters strange omens portending the death of his fianc. His enquiries with the help of Chief Constable Tieh Hu reveal an astounding story, in this tale of men and women struggling to save their true loves.

programme.title: Lover's Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Roving Swordsman
programme.desc: An ambitious evil clan intends to rule the martial arts world. To achieve their goal, they must first steal a secret martial arts manuscript depicting how firearms can be produced. However, a supremely intelligent swordsman Shen Sheng Yi is protecting the manuscript and remains one step ahead of the evil clan.

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Singer Qing Qing and architect Peng Nan are a devoted couple. Qing Qing sacrifices herself to help Peng Nan when his family is going through difficulties and is misunderstood by Peng Nan, leading to their break up. When Peng Nan learns the truth and decides to make up with Qing Qing, he finds out that she is suffering from a terminal illness.

programme.title: The Fake Ghost Catchers
programme.desc: Huan Zhu's ghost seeks help from Fake Ghost Catchers Bao Tuo and Zhou Peng, after a jealous suitor's ghost seeks vengeance by murdering her and now targeting her sister. Together with actor Wu Shun Chao who possesses a supernatural talent, they unite to protect Huan Zhu's sister from both mortal and spectral threats.

programme.title: Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers?
programme.desc: Jenny Hu, Shaw Brothers' gorgeous Chinese-German star, was given her first comedy role in the wild and wacky Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers? Described as "a comedy of belly laughs and chilling murders", it is a unique entry in the Hong Kong theater of the absurd.

programme.title: Killers Five
programme.desc: The Dukes daughter has been kidnapped by the notorious Golden Dragon Hill bandits. A swordman named Yue Zhen Bei is assigned to save her, and expecting many dangers on the journey, Yue garners help from a group of good friends who are also kung fu masters.

programme.title: The Emperor and the Minister
programme.desc: The ingenious imperial scholar Liu Yung always embarrasses Emperor Chien Lung with his quick wit and gift of gab. The emperor purposely sets him up to solve the seemingly unsolvable. However, Liu Yung resolves it easily with wit and style and foils the emperors plot once again.

programme.title: Clan Feuds
programme.desc: Like legendary director Chu Yuan did so often and so successfully, Chang Peng Yi adapted this film from a story by Ku Lung. Following the footsteps of the equally legendary Chang Cheh, Chang also casted the majestic Ti Lung, along with "Venoms Lo Meng and Sun Chien, for a spectacular showcase of mystical Martial Arts Worlds intrigue and consummate Kung Fu.

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: The Swift Knight
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor is dying with no heir to succeed the throne. His brother recalls that he has an illegitimate child with a court lady years ago and palace guards are sent to search for the heir. When the Emperor's nephew hires assassins to kill the child so he can be the successor, the Swift Knight comes to the rescue

programme.title: Mist Over Dream Lake
programme.desc: A young girl Chen is sent away by her parents who are going through divorce, to stay with the Changs. On the Changs farm, she meets their two sons, the youngest daughter and a young artist, and spends a summer with them that she will never forget.

programme.title: The Rebel Intruders
programme.desc: Thousands of displaced refugees rush to the southern towns to avoid the civil war in north China. Three such young men trained with martial arts skills become sworn brothers, and accidentally got involved in the battle of the rebel leaders in town when they save a refugee girl. Can they fight back against the rebel gangs?

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: The Mad Monk is up against the equally legendary scholar-turned-genie, Lu Tung Pin. The duo create havoc as they vie with each other, be it in mirth, magic, women or weapons!

programme.title: The Fighting Fool
programme.desc: Famous Kung Fu Pole master Red Eagle, is kidnapped by a villain one day. His disciple Meng, vows to rescue him. On his way, Meng encounters a greedy but great martial artist who agrees to join him in the rescue. Even though the two have extremely different personalities, they manage to team up and fight the villain in a final showdown.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: Tales of a Eunuch
programme.desc: Tales Of A Eunuch reunites the potent mix of martial arts superstar Gordon Liu, who plays Emperor in cognito Kang Hsi, with the kung-fu comedienne Wang Yu, an anti-Ching revolutionary. It is a film laced with wild barrages of excellent martial arts chiefly choreographed by Yuen Hua and Yuan Pien; Jackie Chan's long-time kung-fu classmates. At one time, Wang was considered to be the next Alexander Fu Sheng.

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: The Dragon Missile
programme.desc: Sima works for a corrupt lord Qin who is suffering from a deadly disease that only a special herb can cure. Qin sends him on an urgent mission to retrieve it, but the task is made more difficult when Sima has to fight off other martial artists who want to steal the cure away from him. He has to fight with his ultimate weapon, the Dragon Missile!

programme.title: River of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her. In an ensuing struggle to free her from his clutches, her husband dies in a car accident. Blamed by her father-in-law for her husbands death, Fang gets chased out of the house and goes back to singing to make a living...

programme.title: Wits Of The Brats
programme.desc: Tou Kuan is a wealthy Kwangtung brat with a good kung fu background, he has only one ambition: to pit his wits against three shady masters of the North. The first, conman Che Tsai. The second, a professional romantic dubbed The Terrific. Terrific introduces Tou Kuan to his third rival, Thief Shih San-shou.

programme.title: Tiger Killer
programme.desc: Wu Song is appointed as chief constable after killing a tiger with his bare hands when drunk. The wife of his brother Wu Da Lang, seduces Wu Song but gets rejected by him, and engages in an affair with a rich man. They poison Wu Da Lang when he finds out about their affair. To avenge his brothers death, Wu Song kills both of them.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Blue and the Black
programme.desc: Set during the Japanese occupation in World War II, a young orphan Tang Qi falls in a love with a young man Chang. However, their love is filled with challenges, from family pressure to the turmoil of war. When Tang Qi was raped, she is expelled from home to become a nightclub singer and embarks on a journey of no return

programme.title: Executioners From Shaolin
programme.desc: The White-Browed Priest supports the brutal Qing government, burning down Shaolin Temple and hunting its disciples. Shaolins Hung falls in love with Fang while escaping the hunt and the couple have a son before Hung is killed by the Priest. To avenge his father, Hungs son creates a new form of martial art combining his parents kung fu styles.

programme.title: The Kid with the Golden Arm
programme.desc: The government hires Yang to escort a cargo of gold to a famine stricken area. The vicious Chi Sha gang, with one of their best fighters, Golden Arm, announce their intention to hijack it by killing one of Yang's employees. As Yang gathers his own team of reputable fighters to protect his cargo, are they strong enough to hold off Golden Arm?

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Brave Archer And His Mate
programme.desc: Guo Jing and Huang Rong raise the son of his sworn brother Yang Kang and named him Yang Guo. To prevent Yang Guo from taking revenge for his fathers death, Huang Rong bans him from learning martial arts. Yang Guo runs away from home in anger and encounters Ouyang Feng, who teaches him the Toad Stance and accidentally unveils his true identity

programme.title: Melody of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s a-go-go era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his wife Gan Lian Zhu are the famous Twin Swords in the martial arts world. One day, they stumble upon a kidnapping plot at the Red Lotus Temple and Lian Zhu is held captive. Wu successfully escapes to find the Gan family for help, not knowing that he is sending them into an ambush by the kidnappers. Can he finally save Lian Zhu?

programme.title: Return of the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: Masked Avengers
programme.desc: Masked killers are wreaking havoc and instilling terror with their vicious weapons of choice: razor-sharp, gut-shattering tridents. Only three fearless fighters dare investigate, leading to mass murder and magnificent martial arts. Chien Hsiao-hou, future co-star of Yuen Woo-ping's THE TAI-CHI MASTER joins the trio to get tri-pierced. The core "Venoms" themselves handle the intricate, always impressive, sometimes awe-inspiring, choreography in this unforgettable exercise in "grand guignol kung-fu."

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows...

programme.title: Go Dog Go! Ep33
programme.desc: Happy Pawtomotiversary / Winner, Winner, Lasagna Dinner - Pawston is celebrating the 40th anniversary of Grandmaw and Grandpaw's Pawtomotive Garage! As a surprise, Tag and Paw decide to track down items to recreate the garage to look like it did when it first opened while the rest of the family distract the Grandpawrents. / Tag and Wind face off in the Lasagna Games for a chance to be Sams new Crew Chief. A series of lasagna-themed games will challenge their speed, fix-it skills, and leadership. But there can only be one winner.

programme.title: Go Dog Go! Ep34
programme.desc: Bites, Camera, Action! / Stay, Dog. Stay! - When Tag finds out that Pawston has a chance to host the Dogcathalon Race, she and Scooch rush around to create a movie to show why their city should host. Unfortunately everything seems to go wrong. Will Tag and Scooch be able to save their movie before time runs out? / When Tag's construction project accidentally damages Frank and Beans house, she invites them to stay with her family during repairs. Tag does her best to keep Frank and Beans busy so they dont get in the Barkers way.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep49
programme.desc: Bunker Break-In/To Catch a Critter - When Branch loses to Poppy at Capture the Flag, he challenges her to break into his bunker and steal Gary, to prove her abilities. Poppy organizes a whacky heist with the help of the Snack Pack. /When Smidge accidentally loses some of the critters Milton cares for, she must try and retrieve them from Trolls Forest.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep50
programme.desc: CJ Wooferbug/What Did I Miss - DJ is excited to give her niece CJ her own wooferbug for her birthday. But the wooferbug proves difficult to transport across Trolls Village. Will DJ be able to get it to CJ before CJs birthday party ends?/When Peppy takes an entire day to get a new haircut, he asks Poppy to fill him in on what he missed. What follows is a series of short sketches, as we explore an average day in Troll Village.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep23
programme.desc: The King Who Would Be King - Fred the Giant Scorpion vows revenge after he reads an untrue story about himself in King Julien's new book.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep24
programme.desc: Are You There Frank? It's Me, King Julien - Frank the Sky God comes to the lemur kingdom to prove his existence and to demand the ultimate sacrifice: King Julien himself.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep28
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Angry Abnormal Atrocities of the Astute Animal Agressors - Stuck in separate camps, Harold and George unleash a hyperintelligent talking possum to scare the pants off of Krupp. What could possibly go wrong?

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep29
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Abysmal Altercation of the Abominable Altitooth - Eager to get the campers out of his hair, Krupp orders them to climb Plummet Peak, where a terrifying creature is rumored to reside.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep51
programme.desc: The Obelisk - When time is running out for Puss to find the Obelisk, he must fight El Moco and finds out who The One from the Great Prophecy is

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep25
programme.desc: Memory Spark / Wondertusk - Kelps learns about memory spark in an attempt to relive a memory of his grandmother. / Kelp and the underwater gang put on a show to showcase their imaginary sparks. As she practices, however, Scallop becomes convinced her tusk has a real spark!

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep25
programme.desc: Flying High / Nest Sweet Nest - Marcus makes a Dew Drop-sized hot-air balloon for Phoebe and the Dews have a blast helping their kids from above, including secretly guiding Lola back to her family, before she accidentally follows Hip-Hop the frog out of the park. / Phoebe makes a pair of glasses for Bob the bird, but when seeing things clearly for the first time gets him lost, the Dews help Bob find his nest before his family arrives for a visit.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep25
programme.desc: Belly Flop - The Riders have to save Elbone when he's swallowed by a giant Sea Gronckle, and Dak's awful cooking might be just the thing to do it.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep11
programme.desc: Catch Me If You Sam / Toy Driver - Its Tag and Scoochs first day of Race Cadets and Sam Whippet tells the Cadets that whoever can catch him in a race will be the new team captain. \ When Mom donates a box of Tags old toys to the new daycare center, Tag decides that the only way to get her box of toys back is to go around town collecting toys to swap out for her toys.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep16
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Harmful Horrors of the Harrowing Hiveschool - After injecting all the teachers with bee DNA, the Melvins run the new "hivemind" of the school. But Ms. Ribble is accidently injected with too much "Bee- NA" and becomes the queen bee, overpowering the Melvins' control. George, Harold and the recently re-hired Vice Principal Krupp must work with the Melvins and stop her from turning everyone into her Zombees.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep17
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Preposterous Pulverizing of the Pestering Poopacabra - In hopes of raising their grades so they can go to Lake Summer Camp, George and Harold must teach Ratrick, their assigned rat, a simple task. But Ratrick runs away into the sewers where he is doused with toxic waste and transformed into Poopacabra! It's now up to the boys and Captain Underpants to stop the beast before it takes over Piqua with its stench, and more importantly, ruins the boys' chances to go to Lake Summer Camp.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep18
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Dastardlys Deed of the Devious Diddlysaurus - George and Harold decide to do an extra credit project on dinosaurs to help their chances of getting summer camp-worthy grades. When Melvin brings in a dinosaur frozen in ice, the boys try to get rid of it. But the ice thaws and they meet Diddlysaurus, a prankster raptor who's huge fans of the boys. He offers to help them with their project if he can pull pranks with them, but when the pranks go too far, the boys and Captain Underpants have to deal with the dino.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep19
programme.desc: We Are Family (Part 1) - Hiccup and Toothless search for other Night Furies.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep20
programme.desc: We Are Family (Part 2) - Hiccup and Toothless are kidnapped and must escape Outcast Island.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep11
programme.desc: Heather Report Part II - Hiccup and the gang infiltrate the outsiders in order to free Heathers parents.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep61
programme.desc: The Big Dumpling - The Uncuddleables have struck the Lil Dumpling baby pageant, replacing all of Baby Corp's super-cute top 5%er babies with not-cute bottom 5%ers. Boss, Tina and their field team race to caravan the 5%ers from their homes to the pageant before Nannycam deploys the nuclear option of unleashing the dangerously cute UBO on stage to salvage a Lil Dumpling win.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep62
programme.desc: The Great Medieval London Fire 1135 - Boss Baby and Tina reject the 5%er system that says the cuter you are, the more love you deserve. Teaming up with the Uncuddleables, the team tries to take down the system from within, forming a resistance of the eight department heads of Baby Corp in the hopes of changing the way we look at Baby Love forever.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep63
programme.desc: Untitled Templeton Project - Fired from Baby Corp and trying to build their own business, Boss Baby and Tina waste all their startup funds immediately, requiring a loan from Banker Baby Benny. In order to receive their seed money and get their company rolling, they have to rebuild the towns faith in a baby who made everyone miss a huge sporting even (and they have to do it on a very limited budget)
